{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-001", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.1", "text_original": "故，小故，有之不必然，無之必不然。體也，若有端。大故，有之必無然，若見之成見也。", "text_normalized": "故，小故，有之不必然，無之必不然。體也，若有端。大故，有之必無然，若見之成見也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-002", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.2", "text_original": "體，若二之一，尺之端也。", "text_normalized": "體，若二之一，尺之端也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-003", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.3", "text_original": "知材，知也者，所以知也，而必知，若明。", "text_normalized": "知材，知也者，所以知也，而必知，若明。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-004", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.4", "text_original": "慮，慮也者以其知有求也，而不必得之，若睨。", "text_normalized": "慮，慮也者以其知有求也，而不必得之，若睨。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-005", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.5", "text_original": "知，知也者以其知過物而能貌之，若見。", "text_normalized": "知，知也者以其知過物而能貌之，若見。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-006", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.6", "text_original": "𢜔，𢜔也者，以其知論物，而其知之也著，若明。", "text_normalized": "𢜔，𢜔也者，以其知論物，而其知之也著，若明。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-007", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.7", "text_original": "仁，愛己者非為用己也，不若愛馬著若明。", "text_normalized": "仁，愛己者非為用己也，不若愛馬著若明。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-008", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.8", "text_original": "義，志以天下為芬，而能能利之，不必用。", "text_normalized": "義，志以天下為芬，而能能利之，不必用。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-009", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.9", "text_original": "禮，貴者公，賤者名，而俱有敬僈焉，等異論也。", "text_normalized": "禮，貴者公，賤者名，而俱有敬僈焉，等異論也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-010", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.10", "text_original": "行，所為不善名，行也。若為善名，巧也，若為盜。", "text_normalized": "行，所為不善名，行也。若為善名，巧也，若為盜。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-011", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.11", "text_original": "實，其志氣之見也，使人如己，不若金聲玉服。", "text_normalized": "實，其志氣之見也，使人如己，不若金聲玉服。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-012", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.12", "text_original": "忠，不利弱子亥，足將入止容。", "text_normalized": "忠，不利弱子亥，足將入止容。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-013", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.13", "text_original": "孝，以親為芬，而能能利親，不必得。", "text_normalized": "孝，以親為芬，而能能利親，不必得。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-014", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.14", "text_original": "信，不以其言之當也，使人視城得金。", "text_normalized": "信，不以其言之當也，使人視城得金。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-015", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.15", "text_original": "佴，與人，遇人，眾𢝺。", "text_normalized": "佴，與人，遇人，眾𢝺。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-016", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.16", "text_original": "訁肙，為是為是之台彼也，弗為也。", "text_normalized": "訁肙，為是為是之台彼也，弗為也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-017", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.17", "text_original": "廉，己惟為之，知其思耳也。", "text_normalized": "廉，己惟為之，知其思耳也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-018", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.18", "text_original": "所令，非身弗行。", "text_normalized": "所令，非身弗行。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-019", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.19", "text_original": "任，為身之所惡，以成人之所急。", "text_normalized": "任，為身之所惡，以成人之所急。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-020", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.20", "text_original": "勇，以其敢於是也，命之，不以其不敢於彼也，害之。", "text_normalized": "勇，以其敢於是也，命之，不以其不敢於彼也，害之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-021", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.21", "text_original": "力，重之謂下，與重，奮也。", "text_normalized": "力，重之謂下，與重，奮也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-022", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.22", "text_original": "生，楹之生，商不可必也。", "text_normalized": "生，楹之生，商不可必也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-023", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.23", "text_original": "臥。", "text_normalized": "臥。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-024", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.24", "text_original": "夢。", "text_normalized": "夢。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-025", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.25", "text_original": "平，惔然。", "text_normalized": "平，惔然。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-026", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.26", "text_original": "利，得是而喜，則是利也。其害也，非是也。", "text_normalized": "利，得是而喜，則是利也。其害也，非是也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-027", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.27", "text_original": "害，得是而惡，則是害也。其利也，非是也。", "text_normalized": "害，得是而惡，則是害也。其利也，非是也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-028", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.28", "text_original": "治，吾事治矣，人有治南北。", "text_normalized": "治，吾事治矣，人有治南北。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-029", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.29", "text_original": "譽之，必其行也，其言之忻。使人督之。", "text_normalized": "譽之，必其行也，其言之忻。使人督之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-030", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.30", "text_original": "誹，必其行也，其言之忻。", "text_normalized": "誹，必其行也，其言之忻。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-031", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.31", "text_original": "舉，告以文名，舉彼實也。", "text_normalized": "舉，告以文名，舉彼實也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-032", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 32, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.32", "text_original": "故言也者，諸口能之出民者也。民若畫俿也。言也，謂言猶石致也。", "text_normalized": "故言也者，諸口能之出民者也。民若畫俿也。言也，謂言猶石致也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-033", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 33, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.33", "text_original": "且，自前曰且，自後曰已，方然亦且。", "text_normalized": "且，自前曰且，自後曰已，方然亦且。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-034", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 34, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.34", "text_original": "若石者也，君，以若名者也。", "text_normalized": "若石者也，君，以若名者也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-035", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 35, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.35", "text_original": "功不待時，若衣裘。", "text_normalized": "功不待時，若衣裘。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-036", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 36, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.36", "text_original": "賞。", "text_normalized": "賞。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-037", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 37, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.37", "text_original": "罪，罪不在禁，惟害無罪殆姑。上報下之功也。", "text_normalized": "罪，罪不在禁，惟害無罪殆姑。上報下之功也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-038", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 38, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.38", "text_original": "罰，上報下之罪也。", "text_normalized": "罰，上報下之罪也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-039", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 39, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.39", "text_original": "侗，二人而俱見是楹也，若事君。", "text_normalized": "侗，二人而俱見是楹也，若事君。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-040", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 40, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.40", "text_original": "久，古今旦莫。", "text_normalized": "久，古今旦莫。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-041", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 41, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.41", "text_original": "宇，東西家南北。", "text_normalized": "宇，東西家南北。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-042", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 42, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.42", "text_original": "窮，或不容尺，有窮。莫不容尺，無窮也。", "text_normalized": "窮，或不容尺，有窮。莫不容尺，無窮也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-043", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 43, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.43", "text_original": "盡，但，止動。", "text_normalized": "盡，但，止動。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-044", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 44, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.44", "text_original": "始，時或有久，或無久，始當無久。", "text_normalized": "始，時或有久，或無久，始當無久。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-045", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 45, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.45", "text_original": "化，若蛙為鶉。", "text_normalized": "化，若蛙為鶉。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-046", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 46, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.46", "text_original": "損，偏去也者，兼之體也。其體或去或存，謂其存者損。", "text_normalized": "損，偏去也者，兼之體也。其體或去或存，謂其存者損。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-047", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 47, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.47", "text_original": "儇，昫民也。", "text_normalized": "儇，昫民也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-048", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 48, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.48", "text_original": "庫，區穴若，斯貌常。", "text_normalized": "庫，區穴若，斯貌常。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-049", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 49, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.49", "text_original": "動，偏祭從者，戶樞免瑟。", "text_normalized": "動，偏祭從者，戶樞免瑟。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-050", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 50, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.50", "text_original": "止，無久之不止，當牛非馬，若矢過楹。有久之不止，當馬非馬，若人過梁。", "text_normalized": "止，無久之不止，當牛非馬，若矢過楹。有久之不止，當馬非馬，若人過梁。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-051", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 51, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.51", "text_original": "必，謂台執者也。若弟兄一然者一不然者，必不必也，是非必也。", "text_normalized": "必，謂台執者也。若弟兄一然者一不然者，必不必也，是非必也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-052", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 52, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.52", "text_original": "同，捷與狂之同長也。", "text_normalized": "同，捷與狂之同長也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-053", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 53, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.53", "text_original": "心中，自是往相若也。", "text_normalized": "心中，自是往相若也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-054", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 54, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.54", "text_original": "厚，惟無所大。", "text_normalized": "厚，惟無所大。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-055", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 55, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.55", "text_original": "圜，規寫攴也。", "text_normalized": "圜，規寫攴也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-056", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 56, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.56", "text_original": "方，矩見攴也。", "text_normalized": "方，矩見攴也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-057", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 57, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.57", "text_original": "倍，二尺與尺但去一。", "text_normalized": "倍，二尺與尺但去一。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-058", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 58, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.58", "text_original": "端，是無同也。", "text_normalized": "端，是無同也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-059", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 59, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.59", "text_original": "有間，謂夾之者也。", "text_normalized": "有間，謂夾之者也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-060", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 60, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.60", "text_original": "間，謂夾者也。尺前于區穴而後於端，不夾于端與區內。及，及非齊之及也。", "text_normalized": "間，謂夾者也。尺前于區穴而後於端，不夾于端與區內。及，及非齊之及也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-061", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 61, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.61", "text_original": "纑閒虛也者，兩木之間，謂其無木者也。", "text_normalized": "纑閒虛也者，兩木之間，謂其無木者也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-062", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 62, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.62", "text_original": "盈，無盈無厚。於尺無所往而不得。", "text_normalized": "盈，無盈無厚。於尺無所往而不得。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-063", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 63, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.63", "text_original": "得二，堅異處不相盈，相非，是相外也。", "text_normalized": "得二，堅異處不相盈，相非，是相外也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-064", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 64, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.64", "text_original": "攖，尺與尺俱不盡，端與端俱盡，尺與或盡或不盡。堅白之攖相盡，體攖不相盡。", "text_normalized": "攖，尺與尺俱不盡，端與端俱盡，尺與或盡或不盡。堅白之攖相盡，體攖不相盡。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-065", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 65, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.65", "text_original": "端。仳，兩有端而後可。", "text_normalized": "端。仳，兩有端而後可。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-066", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 66, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.66", "text_original": "次，無厚而後可。", "text_normalized": "次，無厚而後可。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-067", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 67, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.67", "text_original": "法，意規員三也俱，可以為法。", "text_normalized": "法，意規員三也俱，可以為法。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-068", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 68, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.68", "text_original": "佴，然也者民若法也。", "text_normalized": "佴，然也者民若法也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-069", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 69, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.69", "text_original": "彼，凡牛樞非牛，兩也，無以非也。", "text_normalized": "彼，凡牛樞非牛，兩也，無以非也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-070", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 70, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.70", "text_original": "辯，或謂之牛，或謂之非牛，是爭彼也。是不俱當，不俱當，必或不當，不若當犬。", "text_normalized": "辯，或謂之牛，或謂之非牛，是爭彼也。是不俱當，不俱當，必或不當，不若當犬。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-071", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 71, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.71", "text_original": "欲𩁥其指，智不知其害，是智之罪也。若智之慎文也無遺，於其害也，而猶欲𩁥之，則離之是猶食脯也。騷之利害，未可知也，欲而騷，是不可以所疑止所欲也。廧外之利害，未可知也，趨之而得，則弗趨也，是以所疑止所欲也。觀“為，窮知而𠐴於欲”之理，𩁥脯而非𢜔也，𩁥指而非愚也，所為與不所與為相疑也，非謀也。", "text_normalized": "欲𩁥其指，智不知其害，是智之罪也。若智之慎文也無遺，於其害也，而猶欲𩁥之，則離之是猶食脯也。騷之利害，未可知也，欲而騷，是不可以所疑止所欲也。廧外之利害，未可知也，趨之而得，則弗趨也，是以所疑止所欲也。觀“為，窮知而𠐴於欲”之理，𩁥脯而非𢜔也，𩁥指而非愚也，所為與不所與為相疑也，非謀也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-072", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 72, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.72", "text_original": "已，為衣，成也。治病，亡也。", "text_normalized": "已，為衣，成也。治病，亡也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-073", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 73, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.73", "text_original": "使，令謂，謂也，不必成濕。故也，必待所為之成也。", "text_normalized": "使，令謂，謂也，不必成濕。故也，必待所為之成也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-074", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 74, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.74", "text_original": "名，物，達也。有實必待文多也。命之馬，類也，若實也者必以是名也。命之臧，私也，是名也止於是實也。聲出口，俱有名，若姓、宇。", "text_normalized": "名，物，達也。有實必待文多也。命之馬，類也，若實也者必以是名也。命之臧，私也，是名也止於是實也。聲出口，俱有名，若姓、宇。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-075", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 75, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.75", "text_original": "灑謂狗犬，命也。狗犬，舉也。叱狗，加也。", "text_normalized": "灑謂狗犬，命也。狗犬，舉也。叱狗，加也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-076", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 76, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.76", "text_original": "知，傳受之，聞也。方不障，說也。身觀焉，親也。", "text_normalized": "知，傳受之，聞也。方不障，說也。身觀焉，親也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-077", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 77, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.77", "text_original": "所以謂，名也。所謂，實也。名實耦，合也。志行，為也。", "text_normalized": "所以謂，名也。所謂，實也。名實耦，合也。志行，為也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-078", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 78, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.78", "text_original": "聞，或告之，傳也。身觀焉，親也。", "text_normalized": "聞，或告之，傳也。身觀焉，親也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-079", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 79, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.79", "text_original": "見，時者，體也。二者，盡也。", "text_normalized": "見，時者，體也。二者，盡也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-080", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 80, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.80", "text_original": "古，兵立，反中。志工，正也。臧之為，宜也，非彼必不有，必也。聖者用而勿必，必也者可勿疑。", "text_normalized": "古，兵立，反中。志工，正也。臧之為，宜也，非彼必不有，必也。聖者用而勿必，必也者可勿疑。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-081", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 81, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.81", "text_original": "仗者，兩而勿偏。", "text_normalized": "仗者，兩而勿偏。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-082", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 82, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.82", "text_original": "為，早、台，存也。病，亡也。", "text_normalized": "為，早、台，存也。病，亡也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-083", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 83, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.83", "text_original": "病，亡也。買鬻，易也。霄盡，蕩也。順長，治也。蛙買，化也。", "text_normalized": "病，亡也。買鬻，易也。霄盡，蕩也。順長，治也。蛙買，化也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-084", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 84, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.84", "text_original": "同，二名一實，重同也。不外於兼，體同也。俱處於室，合同也。有以同，類同也。", "text_normalized": "同，二名一實，重同也。不外於兼，體同也。俱處於室，合同也。有以同，類同也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-085", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 85, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.85", "text_original": "異，二必異，二也。不連屬，不體也。不同所，不合也。不有同，不類也。", "text_normalized": "異，二必異，二也。不連屬，不體也。不同所，不合也。不有同，不類也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-086", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 86, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.86", "text_original": "同異交得，於福家良，恕有無也。比度，多少也。免軔還園，去就也。鳥折用桐，堅柔也。劍尤早，死生也。處室子，子母，長少也。兩絕勝，白黑也。中央，旁也。論行學實，是非也。難宿，成未也。兄弟，俱適也。身處志往，存亡也。霍為姓，故也。賈宜，貴賤也。諾，超城員止也。", "text_normalized": "同異交得，於福家良，恕有無也。比度，多少也。免軔還園，去就也。鳥折用桐，堅柔也。劍尤早，死生也。處室子，子母，長少也。兩絕勝，白黑也。中央，旁也。論行學實，是非也。難宿，成未也。兄弟，俱適也。身處志往，存亡也。霍為姓，故也。賈宜，貴賤也。諾，超城員止也。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-087", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 87, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.87", "text_original": "相從、相去、先知、是、可、五色。長短、前後、輕重援。", "text_normalized": "相從、相去、先知、是、可、五色。長短、前後、輕重援。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-088", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 88, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.88", "text_original": "執服難成，言務成之，九則求執之。", "text_normalized": "執服難成，言務成之，九則求執之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-089", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 89, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.89", "text_original": "法，法取同，觀巧傳法，取此擇讀彼，問故觀宜。以人之有黑者有不黑者也，止黑人；與以有愛於人有不愛于人，心愛人，是孰宜心？彼舉然者，以為此其然也，則舉不然者而問之。", "text_normalized": "法，法取同，觀巧傳法，取此擇讀彼，問故觀宜。以人之有黑者有不黑者也，止黑人；與以有愛於人有不愛于人，心愛人，是孰宜心？彼舉然者，以為此其然也，則舉不然者而問之。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3__seg-090", "work_id": "mozi", "section_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i", "source_id": "mozi-033-exposition-of-canon-i__chinesenotes-mozi-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 90, "canonical_ref": "墨子 033.90", "text_original": "若聖人有非而不非，正五諾，皆人於知有說。過五諾，若負，無直無說。用五諾，若自然矣。", "text_normalized": "若聖人有非而不非，正五諾，皆人於知有說。過五諾，若負，無直無說。用五諾，若自然矣。", "notes": ""}
